585
00:45:26,720 --> 00:45:28,393
No, they attract mice.

586
00:45:30,280 --> 00:45:31,918
People look different at home.

587
00:45:32,240 --> 00:45:33,275
In what way?

588
00:45:34,080 --> 00:45:35,559
Off guard.

589
00:45:39,040 --> 00:45:40,269
Should I be on my guard?

590
00:45:40,360 --> 00:45:41,395
No.

591
00:45:41,600 --> 00:45:43,318
I'm a man who drinks tea.

592
00:45:56,960 --> 00:45:59,190
When the trouble dies down, I'll go.

593
00:46:06,560 --> 00:46:08,551
