594
00:46:09,440 --> 00:46:11,078
Late, I'd say.

595
00:46:14,640 --> 00:46:16,278
So not until the morning then.

596
00:46:18,760 --> 00:46:21,036
Yes, I'd say I'll be here till morning.

597
00:46:28,520 --> 00:46:29,590
