609
00:49:23,480 --> 00:49:25,073
The whole fucking thing.

610
00:49:25,880 --> 00:49:27,109
Fucking life.

611
00:49:28,120 --> 00:49:29,315
Business.

612
00:49:31,800 --> 00:49:33,313
I found you.

613
00:49:35,200 --> 00:49:36,520
